OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1771861676
OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,FThe rising use of AI by fashion
OL,7,Fretailers contributed to Citizens
OL,8,FAdvice receiving almost 18,000
OL,9,Fcomplaints from customers last year `
OL,10,Fa surge of 21% on a year earlier, it
OL,11,Fhas reported.
OL,13,FThe advisory service said it was
OL,14,Fhelping a consumer with a fashion
OL,15,Fpurchase every seven minutes, finding
OL,16,Fthat the ever-increasing use of AI
OL,17,F"makes it easier for scammers to trick
OL,18,Fpeople into buying items that look
OL,19,Fnothing like the images advertised".
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@cO]
