OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,FAccording to the charity's consumer
OL,7,Fservice, 82% of complaints about
OL,8,Fclothes, shoes and accessories related
OL,9,Fto online orders (14,487), while 14%
OL,10,Fwere bought in-store (2,569).
OL,12,FWomen's clothing caused the most
OL,13,Fheadaches, making up almost half (48%)
OL,14,Fof all complaints (8,508), while men's
OL,15,Fclothing made up 20% (3,523).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
