OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1771861676
OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,FThe most common five issues suffered
OL,7,Fby fashion buyers last year were
OL,8,Ffaulty goods, making up 18% of all
OL,9,Fcomplaints, delivery failures or
OL,10,Fdelays (13%), trouble returning
OL,11,Funwanted goods (12%), breach of
OL,12,Fcontract (9%) and poor customer
OL,13,Fservice (6%).
OL,15,FOf last year's complaints, one in 13
OL,16,Finvolved scams, including shoppers
OL,17,Fthinking they were buying items from
OL,18,FUK-based companies, due to their
OL,19,Fadvertising.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1771861676
OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,FInstead, consumers had received poor
OL,7,Fquality items that were not as
OL,8,Fpictured, and, when they tried to
OL,9,Freturn them, were asked to pay
OL,10,Fexpensive fees to send them to an
OL,11,Faddress overseas.
OL,13,FOne consumer, Hannah, a mother in her
OL,14,F30s from the East Midlands who did not
OL,15,Fwant her surname published, told
OL,16,FCitizens Advice she was Christmas
OL,17,Fshopping online when she saw a jacket
OL,18,Fshe liked advertised at half price.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1771861676
OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,FThe company selling the jacket claimed
OL,7,Fit was based in London's Covent
OL,8,FGarden, and Hannah bought it for #35
OL,9,Fusing a debit card.
OL,11,FHannah said: "The jacket took a few
OL,12,Fweeks to come and when it did, it was
OL,13,Fa totally different material and
OL,14,Fcolour, and not as premium as it was
OL,15,Fpictured. The pockets were different
OL,16,Fand it had massive plastic buttons,
OL,17,Fbut the one in the photograph had nice
OL,18,Fmetal ones. It even smelled cheap."
OL,20,FHannah emailed the company to complain
OL,21,Fand request a refund.
OL,26,@sD@NOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1771861676
OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,FShe said: "The service felt very
OL,7,Fdifferent to any other clothing
OL,8,Fcompany I'd dealt with. They asked for
OL,9,Fpictures of the jacket I'd received
OL,10,Fand I thought 'this company sent the
OL,11,Fitem to me, surely they should know
OL,12,Fwhat it looks like'. They also emailed
OL,13,Fme on Boxing Day.
OL,15,F"They said I could return the jacket
OL,16,Fif I sent it to China at my own
OL,17,Fexpense, it left me fuming. I looked
OL,18,Fup the cost of shipping and it was
OL,19,Fabout #15. The website clearly stated
OL,20,Fit was a UK business, which was
OL,21,Fdeceptive."
OL,26,@nD@KOUwD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1771861676
OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,FHannah reported the incident to the
OL,7,FCitizens Advice Consumer Service, and
OL,8,Fwas able to get a full refund through
OL,9,Fher bank, which covered the cost.
OL,10,FEventually, the company did issue a
OL,11,Frefund itself.
OL,13,FJane Parsons, consumer spokeswoman at
OL,14,FCitizens Advice, said: "Shopping
OL,15,Fshould be simple and stress-free, but
OL,16,Fevery year we hear from thousands of
OL,17,Ffrustrated people who have a tough
OL,18,Ftime trying to resolve issues with
OL,19,Fretailers and sellers.
OL,26,@vD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1771861676
OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,F"Consumers face all kinds of problems
OL,7,Ffrom receiving faulty items, to
OL,8,Fwaiting weeks for deliveries and poor
OL,9,Fcustomer service. Plus, the ever-
OL,10,Fincreasing use of AI makes it easier
OL,11,Ffor scammers to trick people into
OL,12,Fbuying items that look nothing like
OL,13,Fthe images advertised.
OL,15,F"It's important consumers know what
OL,16,Fsteps to take before they part with
OL,17,Ftheir cash or after there's an issue.
OL,18,FIt can make all the difference in
OL,19,Favoiding a trap or getting a refund."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
