PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1771861676
OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,FMike Andrews, national coordinator of
OL,7,Fthe National Trading Standards eCrime
OL,8,FTeam, said: "Online retail scams leave
OL,9,Fshoppers out of pocket and
OL,10,Funderstandably frustrated.
OL,12,F"What appears to be a genuine retailer
OL,13,Fcan turn out to be a fake website, a
OL,14,Fmisleading advert or goods that never
OL,15,Farrive.
OL,17,F"Criminals are increasingly using
OL,18,Fprofessional-looking sites and
OL,19,Fconvincing promotions to exploit
OL,20,Fpeople's confidence in well-known
OL,21,Fbrands.
OL,26,@pD@MOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1771861676
OL,3,CAI contributes to spike in fashion
OL,4,Csales complaints to Citizens Advice
OL,6,F"We would encourage consumers to pause
OL,7,Fbefore buying online ` check the
OL,8,Fretailer using a URL checker from a
OL,9,Freputable website like Get Safe
OL,10,FOnline, be cautious of offers that
OL,11,Fseem too good to be true, avoid buying
OL,12,Fdirectly through social media adverts
OL,13,Fand always pay by card or a secure
OL,14,Fpayment platform."
OL,16,FUK consumer laws are difficult to
OL,17,Fenforce when sellers turn out to be
OL,18,Fbased overseas.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@RO]
